{"id": 1754, "title": "Ticket #1754: Warn the user if a priority category has no nodes assigned to it", "description": "<blockquote>\nI just noticed a DAG where the user had used the node name as the priority category, and didn't assign any nodes to that category.  This means that their priority statement would end up having no effect.\n\n<p>Currently there is no warning for this case, but I think there should be.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2011-Jan-13 15:00:01 by wenger:</em> <br/>\n\nJust finished coding and documenting this -- there is also a warning if a category has no throttle set.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1755\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1755'); return false;\" title=\"Have a -strict flag that turns some warnings into fatal errors\">#1755</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nHave a -strict flag that turns some warnings into fatal errors</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Jan-13 14:50</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/ca65df5c6770a1f89fe1a91dda7e48725878ec43\">[25831]</a></span>: Fixed gittrac <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1754\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1754'); return false;\" title=\"Warn the user if a priority category has no nodes assigned to it\">#1754</a></span>: we now give a warning if a node category has no nodes assigned to it, or no throttle set.  (By Kent Wenger )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Jan-13 14:50</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/a995ed846e39bc1e724c5a977bb62818d6419268\">[19946]</a></span>: Fixed gittrac <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1754\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1754'); return false;\" title=\"Warn the user if a priority category has no nodes assigned to it\">#1754</a></span>: we now give a warning if a node category has no nodes assigned to it, or no throttle set.  (By Kent Wenger )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2011-Jan-13 15:01", "status": "resolved", "created": "2010-Nov-04 10:14", "fixed_version": "2010-Nov-04 10:14", "broken_version": "v070504", "priority": "1", "subsystem": "Dag", "assigned_to": "wenger", "derived_from": "", "creator": "wenger", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "wenger@cs.wisc.edu,psilord@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}